snippet.title: Witness Says 'NO BRUISES' On Amber Heard As Johnny Depp Trial Continues
snippet.description:
Another witness says that Amber Heard had no bruises as the Johnny Depp trial continues against the sun.
There were no signs of any marks, scratches, swelling or bruises on Amber Heard’s face in the days immediately after she alleged she was hit by Johnny Depp, one of his closest friends has claimed.
